metadata.name: FETUS
metadata.description:
There are so many objects around me...
It's all so tiring...
To calm down a bit, I painted them all in the same color and pattern...
I'm painting myself....
To escape the thoughts...
Like a butterfly, I wait in a cocoon. I create my own cocoon.
Just like in my mother's womb...
I'm waiting for the time to run out.
